channel.title: Cryptchaosv2 Revised 10K DOWNLOADS, Pictures, Cleaner Files LOOK!
channel.description:
(Note: I uploaded it on Rapidshare since uppit is having some problems)
[size=5]Cryptchaosv2 is here![/size]
[b]OVER 4000 DOWNLOADS![/b]
[size=5]ATTENTION![/size] [b]This will be my LAST source release of Cryptchaos now, I have quit silabsoft and now will only make improvements to the Cryptchaos server in general and will NOT release future updates of Cryptchaos to the public. The download links will still be available for v1 and v2. I no longer offer support tfor any version of Cryptchaos and will not be releasing any more. Sorry for people that liked Cryptchaos. I have QUIT silabsoft also.[/b]
[size=5]FOR THE EXTREME NOOBS![/size] [code]When im compiling.. THe results are always: Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note:Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details.
Done![/code] [size=5]MEANS ITS WORKING PROPERLY![/size]
_________________________________UPDATES_________________________________
- Made new Team pk - Made new Smithing area - Made barrier connecting smithing to mining - Mining area/Smithing area are now 100% Complete - Fixed up shops - Moved shop locations - Redid Starter - Added requirements to bows and armor - Added new 10 wave Jad mini-game with Firecape restrictions - Added GS-mini stance - Added new 1v1 PK area - Fixed Super sets (70%) - Fixed food glitch - [b]CLEANED CLIENT.JAVA AND OTHER FILES[/b] - Added Fishing - Fixed Fishing (Added timers) - Fixed Fishing x2 (Added level requirements, equipment requirements) - Added Working Skulls (Silab webclient only) Appears when you kill someone - Fixed Jad mini-game tele glitch - Added text to 'Illegal' barrage spells not missable - Added new rewards for Thieve. (Same location will change in v3) - Added even more SYI blocker - GSmini was taken out [i]PLEASE NOTE THIS IS A MUCH SMALLER LIST ALOT OF SMALLER UPDATES WERE MADE[/i] __________________________________________________________________________
Commands
[b]Owner commands (Co-owner)[/b] [i]::banuser ::ipban ::pickup ::kick ::pnpc ::xrichie ::xteleto ::xteletome ::xteleall ::notedbarrows ::players ::ground ::master ::pure ::empty ::sweet ::rich[/i]
[b]Administrator Commands[/b] [i]::banuser ::ipban ::kick ::pnpc ::xteleto ::xteletome ::notedbarrows ::brunes2 (10000 Barrage Runes) ::players ::ground ::empty ::sweet ::rich ::runes[/i]
[b]Moderator Commands[/b] [i]::banuser ::kick ::xteleto ::xteletome ::notedbarrows ::starter ::brunes (1000 Barrage runes) ::players ::ground ::empty ::rich ::runes [/i]
[b]Regular Commands[/b] [i]::starter ::players ::ground ::brunes (1000 barrage runes) ::empty ::runes[/i]
(Note: Only Owner/Co-owners are able to do ::master and ::pure)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The next verison is Cryptchaos v1.5 which will have much cleaner files as I have to admit they are not the most tidy because its my first server, more glitches fixed, different locations on some places ect. All server bases I use come with 'roflmao456 auto restarter' all ready configured for you to use just click it and set when you want your server to be restarted. Please read the 'README!' .txt file on the base after downloading Thanks and I hope you like it![/i]
